  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-2 Minimal clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels for each factor. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed and documented. Decision: Accepted on the basis of complete structured evidence with no outstanding gaps.",
